                            <p>Hi, I'm Jason. I dreamed of becoming a scientist when I was 10, and dreamed of becoming a teacher when I'm 18, and an entrepreneur when 23. I'm an App Developer now. My ideal is to start a business with like-minded friends by running a broad software company. And my biggest dream is to live happily with family everyday. I believe life is a process, not only the result; as long as we target the top of the mountain and keep going, we all will have a wonderful journey.</p>
                         
